{
  "id": "adv_card_ymk_01_03",
  "title": "雪ミク 3話 ようこそ函館へ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ミクの提案で、北海道最終日は函館観光に決まった）\n（見所の多い街や施設を巡り――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（On Miku's suggestion‚ we decided to spend our last day in Hokkaido sightseeing in Hakodate）\n（We toured the streets and facilities with many attractions——）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0086620649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "五稜郭、圧巻だったわね。本当に綺麗な星の形を\nしてるんだもの。素直に感動しちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Goryokaku was impressive. It really has\na beautiful star shape. I was genuinely moved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9129704159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "知れば知るほど、興味深い建築物よね\n箱館戦争の折は旧幕府軍の本拠として機能し――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more you learn about it‚ the more interesting this building is\nDuring the Battle of Hakodate‚ it functioned as the headquarters of the former shogunate army——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "新撰組、鬼の副長・土方歳三が最後に辿り着いた場所\nその後、彼は最後まで前線に立って戦い抜き……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The place where Toshizo Hijikata‚ the demon vice―commander of the Shinsengumi‚ finally arrived\nAfter that‚ he fought on the front lines until the very end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0107955298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新撰組、好きだったんですか？\nく、詳しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you a fan of the Shinsengumi?\nWow‚ you know a lot of details",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0107955298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "というより、歴史上のリーダー達を尊敬しているのよ\n新撰組に限らず、国内外問わずね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather‚ I respect leaders throughout history\nNot just the Shinsengumi‚ but both domestic and foreign ones",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.6827001573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私だってリズノワのリーダーだもの\n学ぶべきことは沢山あるはず。だからいろいろ調べたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I'm the leader of LizNoir too\nThere must be a lot to learn. That's why I researched various things",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.769744702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そうやって調べていくうちに\n気付いたら歴史にも詳しくなってきたと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so as you were researching\nYou ended up becoming knowledgeable about history too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5888.070646799995,
          "startTime": 64.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.790982787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-ymk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　莉央ちゃん、何か落としたよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Rio‚ did you drop something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.790982787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4909807525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4909807525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.7211870058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、もしかして、今披露した知識って……\nこれは……五稜郭の観光パンフレット？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ could it be that the knowledge you just shared…\nThis is… a tourist pamphlet for the Goryokaku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7211870058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.0898493949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そろそろどこかお店に入らない！？\nお腹も空いてきちゃったし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S―shouldn't we go into a store soon!?\nI'm starting to get hungry too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（ごまかした。莉央さん、いつになくはしゃいでるな）\n（普段と違う一面を見られるのも、旅先ならではだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She dodged the question. Rio seems unusually excited）\n（Seeing a different side of her is also a pleasure unique to traveling）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4359722003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さん！\n何よその生暖かい眼差しは！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}!\nWhat's with that lukewarm look!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3333312989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ！　ご飯にしましょう！\nミク、どこかオススメはあるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N―nothing! Let's get something to eat!\nMiku‚ do you have any recommendations?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5344081426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-ymk002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　うん、じゃあ北海道グルメだね？　任せて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Yeah‚ how about Hokkaido cuisine? Leave it to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5344081426,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8965.591857399999,
          "startTime": 112.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 112.1000094097
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 112.1000094097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、食事を済ませて観光を続けた俺達は）\n（最後に函館山へ向かった――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After that‚ we finished our meal and continued sightseeing）\n（Finally‚ we headed to Mount Hakodate——）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8000005087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 119.2297443574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗……\nこれが有名な、函館の夜景なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Beautiful…\nSo this is the famous night view of Hakodate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 124.614030316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "函館に来たら見るべきって言われている理由が\n分かった気がするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I understand why they say\nyou must see this when you come to Hakodate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3666781108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 129.182765709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "それに……なんだか似てる気がする\nステージの上から見える景色に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… it feels similar to something\nThe view from the stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7333447774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ステージの上から……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From the stage…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2507765478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 137.4164909627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そう\nペンライトの光みたいって思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes\nDon't you think it looks like penlight lights?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6000175476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 141.242840253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_03-ymk003.m4a",
      "text": "似てると思う\n光の海みたいな、眩しいあの景色と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think they're similar\nThat dazzling scenery like a sea of light…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkadeck-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
